 book includes numerous examples of the writings and visual art of Masses women and a series of biographical/bibliographical sketches designed to aid other researchers.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aAfrican literaturexStudy and teaching. 0aAuthors, American - 20th century - Biography. 0aAuthors, American. 0aFolklorezAfricavBibliography. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/74026640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780292780224423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780292780224/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles